#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
msgid ""
"State cookies are used to support authorization code flow completion.\n"
"When an authorization code flow is started, Quarkus creates a state cookie and a matching `state` query parameter, before redirecting the user to the OIDC provider."
msgstr ""

#: _versions/main/guides/security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc
msgid "When the user is redirected back to Quarkus to complete the authorization code flow, Quarkus expects the request URI to include the `state` query parameter that matches the current state cookie value."
